Troubleshooting
Build Errors
Error
Solution
ANDROID_HOME not found
Set environment variable: export ANDROID_HOME=/path/to/sdk
Gradle build failed
Run cordova clean android then rebuild
Java version mismatch
Ensure Java 11+: java -version
SDK not found
Install Android SDK via Android Studio
Permission denied
On Linux: sudo usermod -a -G android $USER
Installation Errors
Error
Solution
Unknown app
Enable "Unknown Sources": Settings > Security
Installation failed
Clear app cache, restart phone
Permission denied
Grant microphone permission in app settings
App crashes
Check device has Android 7.0+
Runtime Errors
Error
Solution
Microphone not working
Grant microphone permission in Settings
No audio recorded
Check microphone is not muted
App freezes
Restart app, clear cache
Storage full
Delete old recordings, free up space
